metadata.name: Lazy Sloth #1
metadata.description:
The Lazy Sloths, 9,973 Lazy and sleepy heads, unique digital collectibles who are hanging on the tree of Ethereum blockchain. Your Lazy Sloth doubles as your DAO The50 membership card, and grants access to members-only benefits! 

 Our collective is committed to help new NFT Artists to succeed in the Metaverse. We're building an inclusive and diverse society.
